    <title type="html"><![CDATA[使用VirtualBox搭建linux环境]]></title>
    <link href="http://lpisces.github.io/blog/2013/05/03/shi-yong-virtualboxda-jian-linuxhuan-jing/"/>
    <updated>2013-05-03T21:25:00+08:00</updated>
